This project is a fork of and builds upon the following works:

1. qwen3-tts.cpp (original)
   Author:  predict-woo
   Source:  https://github.com/predict-woo/qwen3-tts.cpp
   License: No license specified by upstream author.
            This fork was created from the publicly available source with the
            intent of open-source distribution under the MIT License above.
            Original authorship is acknowledged and credited here.

2. Qwen3-TTS Model Weights
   Author:  Alibaba Cloud — Qwen Team
   Source:  https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-0.6B-Base
            https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3-TTS-12Hz-1.7B-Base
            https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3-TTS
   License: Apache License 2.0
            https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
   Note:    The model weights themselves are NOT included in this repository.
            They must be downloaded separately and are subject to the
            Apache 2.0 license terms set by Alibaba Cloud.

3. GGML
   Author:  Georgi Gerganov and the ggml authors
   Source:  https://github.com/ggml-org/ggml
   License: MIT License
            Copyright (c) 2023-2026 The ggml authors
            Full license text: ggml/LICENSE

4. WavTokenizer (vocoder architecture reference)
   Author:  Shengpeng Ji et al.
   Source:  https://github.com/jishengpeng/WavTokenizer
   Note:    The vocoder architecture implemented in this project is based on
            the WavTokenizer design. No source code from WavTokenizer was
            directly copied; the implementation is an independent C++/GGML
            port derived from the model weights and architecture description.

